data.description: Welcome to a luxurious, brand-new home nestled in the serene landscapes of Copperas Cove! This exceptional property offers a unique blend of modern comfort and rustic charm. It is perfectly situated within a gated community, and spreads across a sprawling 5 acres of picturesque countryside. Step inside, where you’ll discover an elegantly designed open floor plan that creates an inviting atmosphere. The living room features a stunning fireplace and large windows that allow natural light to stream in. The kitchen offers brand-new stainless steel appliances, a center island, and abundant cabinet and counter space. The master bedroom is complete with a generous layout and a spa-like ensuite bathroom with a luxurious garden tub, separate shower, and dual vanity. This property presents a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to experience the beauty of country living at its finest. Don’t wait – schedule your private tour today!
